{"tid":1529322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"真係要比掌聲各位爸媽 多謝你地 我愛你地","createTime":"2019-09-01T17:01:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T00:40:08.000Z","uid":66390,"like":58,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ff995c1da9b785ae028535d03c3ce84f8ce2f49e","tid":1529322,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:01:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jj1i9G6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjj1i9G6.png&h=8bc71a1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我諗好多係東涌既仔女<br />\n都以為死撚緊 行去欣澳=死路一條<br />\n<br />\n但大家一呼百應 我真係好感動<br />\n個感覺係 又團結起上來<br />\n<br />\n見到車隊係咁駛入<br />\n好似拍戲咁<br />\n一個一個咁接放學<br />\n<br />\n6月到呢家 無家長<br />\n被捕人數一定倍增<br />\n<br />\n今日學識一個term <span style=\"color: gold;\">「執蛋」</span><br />\n受傷既仔女叫「爛蛋」<br />\n真係好有趣 我愛大家"},{"pid":"628b93eb47894027f68778b0dcd4ad60bee100fe","tid":1529322,"uid":66390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:02:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Dunkirk 鄧寇克大行動</span></span>"},{"pid":"2d4f5dfe96ba11fd2e00b5dfef949c12c3e1e5ec","tid":1529322,"uid":219564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:03:24.000Z","msg":"建議9月8日百萬人大遊行，請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案，宣揚攬炒精神﹗<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1510235\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1510235</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6461eb4999a58a2cb989dbb076e6500fbb6eced8","tid":1529322,"uid":232186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:03:38.000Z","msg":"感激不盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"101cee0d45271381a80b1b0625a6879951382efc","tid":1529322,"uid":266755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:03:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f5c582c74d0dd37667ea18f31405a27fdcc94b54","t